00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,300
Aku bisa sendiri

13
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,018
pergi mandi sana

14
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:47,600
nanti terlambat

15
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,000
Aku bisa ambil cuti sehari untuk menjagamu.

16
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:54,360
